{"title":"故国游","authors":["非马"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故国游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么样的浪漫豪情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们争先攀登"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸嶙峋的背脊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去瞻望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动调距的镜头里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萋萋的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒万里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙的骸骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明与"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野蛮的争斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何其艰烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看这长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒起伏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无止无休"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫禁城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何等残酷的刑罚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被推出午门斩首的老臣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须踉跄走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条长廊又一条长廊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个宫院又一个宫院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道宫门又一道宫门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲折的宦途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迢遥的绝路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谗言镣铐的沉重脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在凹凸不平的砖地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依稀仍可辨识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回　音　壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有求必应而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们并不在乎我们听到的回音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是模糊卑微的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不来自上帝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八六年九月于芝加哥"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}